    - s390/dasd: fix panic for failed online processing
    - ACPI / scan: Initialize status to ACPI_STA_DEFAULT
    - blk-mq: count the hctx as active before allocating tag
    - scsi: aic94xx: fix an error code in aic94xx_init()
