    - mtd: rawnand: qcom: wait for desc completion in all BAM channels
    - clk: rockchip: fix clk_i2sout parent selection bits on rk3399
    - clk: npcm7xx: fix memory allocation
    - PM / clk: signedness bug in of_pm_clk_add_clks()
